msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:1.1"
msgid "Taisho vol.23, no.1437"
msgstr "Taisho vol.23, no.1437"

#. </p><p class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:2.1"
msgid "Sarvāstivāda Bhikkhunī Pātimokkha"
msgstr "Sarvāstivāda Bhikkhunī Pātimokkha"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:3.1"
msgid "十誦比丘尼波羅提木叉戒本一卷"
msgstr ""

#. </h1><p class="subheading">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:4.1"
msgid "宋長干寺沙門釋法顯集出"
msgstr ""

#. </p></div><h2>
#. <span class="add"><a id="intro" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:5.1"
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Introduction"

#. </a></span>
#. </h2><h3>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:6.1"
msgid "說法章"
msgstr ""

#. </h3><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:7.1"
msgid "大德尼僧聽。冬時一月過少一夜。餘有一夜三月在。老死至近。佛法欲滅。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h3>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:8.1"
msgid "第二教戒章"
msgstr ""

#. </h3><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:9.1"
msgid "諸大德。為得道故。一心勤精進。所以者何。諸佛一心勤精進故。得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。何況餘善道法。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h3>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:10.1"
msgid "第三會坐章"
msgstr ""

#. </h3><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:11.1"
msgid "未受具足者已出。僧今和合。先作何事<span class=\"t-note\">(一人答布薩說波羅提木叉)</span>諸大德。不來諸比丘尼。說欲及清淨。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h3>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:12.1"
msgid "第四供養章"
msgstr ""

#. </h3><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:13.1"
msgid "合十指爪掌　　供養釋師子"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:13.2"
msgid "我今欲說戒　　僧當一心聽"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:13.3"
msgid "乃至小罪中　　心應大怖畏"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:13.4"
msgid "有罪一心悔　　後更莫復犯"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:13.5"
msgid "心馬馳惡道　　放逸難禁制"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:13.6"
msgid "佛說切戒行　　亦如利轡勒"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:13.7"
msgid "佛口說教誡　　善者能信受"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:13.8"
msgid "是人馬調順　　能破煩惱軍"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:13.9"
msgid "若不受教<span class=\"gaiji\">勅<!--gaiji,敕,1[束*力],2&#x52C5;,3--> </span>　　亦不愛樂戒"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:13.10"
msgid "是人馬不調　　沒在煩惱軍"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:13.11"
msgid "若人守護戒　　如犛牛愛尾"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:13.12"
msgid "繫心不放逸　　亦如猴著鎖"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:13.13"
msgid "日夜常精進　　求實智慧故"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:13.14"
msgid "是人佛法中　　能得清淨命"
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><h3>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:14.1"
msgid "第五和眾章"
msgstr ""

#. </h3><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:15.1"
msgid "大德尼僧聽。今十五日布薩說波羅提木叉。若僧時到僧忍聽。僧一心作布薩說波羅提木叉。如是白。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h3>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:16.1"
msgid "第六淨眾章"
msgstr ""

#. </h3><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:17.1"
msgid "諸大德。今共作布薩說波羅提木叉。僧一心善聽。有罪者發露。無罪者默然。默然故。當知諸大德清淨。如一一比丘尼問答。是比丘尼眾中三唱亦如是。若有比丘尼。如是比丘尼眾中第三唱。憶有罪不發露。得故妄語罪。諸大德。故妄語罪。佛說遮道法。比丘尼於此中欲求清淨。憶有罪應發露。發露則安隱。不發露罪益深。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="3"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:18.1"
msgid "諸大德。已說波羅提木叉序。今問諸大德。是中清淨不。第二第三亦如是問。是中清淨不。諸大德。是中清淨。默然故。是事如是持。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h2>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pj" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:19.1"
msgid "8 pārājika rules"
msgstr "8 pārājika rules"

#. </a></span>
#. </h2><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:20.1"
msgid "諸大德。是八波羅夷法。半月半月波羅提木叉中說。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pj1" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:21.1"
msgid "pārājika 1"
msgstr "pārājika 1"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:22.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。同入比丘尼學法。不捨戒戒羸不出。行婬法乃至共畜生。是比丘尼犯波羅夷。不應共住。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pj2" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:23.1"
msgid "pārājika 2"
msgstr "pārājika 2"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="4"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:24.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。若聚落若空地。不與取。名盜物。如不與物取故。若王若王等。若捉若殺。若縛若擯。若輸金罪。若言。汝小兒汝賊汝癡。如是相。不與物取。是比丘尼犯波羅夷。不應共住。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pj3" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:25.1"
msgid "pārājika 3"
msgstr "pārājika 3"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="5"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:26.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。若人若似人。故自手奪命。若持刀與。若教死若讚死。作是言。人用惡活為。死勝生。隨彼心樂死。種種因緣教死讚死。是人因是事死。是比丘尼犯波羅夷。不應共住。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pj4" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:27.1"
msgid "pārājika 4"
msgstr "pārājika 4"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="6"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:28.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。不知不見。空無過人法。自言。我如是知如是見。是比丘尼後時若問若不問。貪利養故。不知言知。不見言見。空誑妄語。除增上慢。是比丘尼犯波羅夷。不應共住。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pj5" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:29.1"
msgid "pārājika 5"
msgstr "pārājika 5"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="7"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:30.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。有漏心聽漏心男子。髮際已下至膝腕已上。<span class=\"gaiji\">却<!--gaiji,卻,1[去*ㄗ],2&#x5374;,3--> </span>衣順摩逆摩。牽推按搯抱上抱下。是比丘尼犯波羅夷。不應共住。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pj6" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:31.1"
msgid "pārājika 6"
msgstr "pārājika 6"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="8"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:32.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。有漏心聽漏心男子。捉手捉衣共立共語。共期入屏覆處。待男子來。與身如白衣女。以此八事示貪著相。是比丘尼犯波羅夷。不應共住。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pj7" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:33.1"
msgid "pārājika 7"
msgstr "pārājika 7"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="9"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:34.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。知比丘尼犯重罪。覆藏乃至一夜。是比丘尼。知彼比丘尼若退若住若滅若去。後作是言。我亦先知是比丘尼犯如是如是罪。但不欲自舉。不欲向僧說。或有人言。云何妹自污其姊。是比丘尼犯波羅夷。不應共住。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pj8" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:35.1"
msgid "pārājika 8"
msgstr "pārājika 8"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="10"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:36.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。知是比丘。一心和合僧。如法作不見擯。獨一無二。無伴無侶。不休不息。便往隨順。諸比丘尼。應如是諫是比丘尼。是比丘。一心和合僧。如法作不見擯。獨一無二。無伴無侶。不休不息。汝莫隨順是比丘。諸比丘尼如是諫時。堅持是事不捨者。諸比丘尼應第二第三諫。令捨是事故。第二第三諫時。若捨是事善。若不捨者。是比丘尼犯波羅夷。不應共住。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="11"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:37.1"
msgid "諸大德。已說八波羅夷法。若比丘尼犯一一法。是比丘尼不得共住。不得共事。如前後亦如是。是比丘尼犯波羅夷。不應共住。今問諸大德。是中清淨不。第二第三亦如是問。是中清淨不。諸大德。是中清淨。默然故。是事如是持。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h2>
#. <span class="add"><a id="ss" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:38.1"
msgid "17 saṅghādisesa rules"
msgstr "17 saṅghādisesa rules"

#. </a></span>
#. </h2><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:39.1"
msgid "諸大德。是十七僧伽婆尸沙法。半月半月波羅提木叉中說。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="ss1" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:40.1"
msgid "saṅghadisesa 1"
msgstr "saṅghadisesa 1"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="12"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:41.1"
msgid "若比丘尼行媒法。若持男意語女。持女意語男。若為婦事若私通事。乃至一會時。是法初犯僧伽婆尸沙可沙可悔過。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="ss2" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:42.1"
msgid "saṅghadisesa 2"
msgstr "saṅghadisesa 2"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="13"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:43.1"
msgid "若比丘尼惡瞋故。以無根波羅夷法。謗無波羅夷比丘尼。欲破彼梵行。是比丘尼後時若問若不問。知是事無根。是比丘尼住瞋故。作是語者。是法初犯僧伽婆尸沙可沙可悔過。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="ss3" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:44.1"
msgid "saṅghadisesa 3"
msgstr "saṅghadisesa 3"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="14"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:45.1"
msgid "若比丘尼惡瞋故。異分中取片若似片事。以波羅夷法謗。欲破彼比丘尼梵行。是比丘尼後時。若問若不問。知是片似片事。是比丘尼住瞋故。作是語者。是法初犯僧伽婆尸沙可沙可悔過。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="ss4" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:46.1"
msgid "saṅghadisesa 4"
msgstr "saṅghadisesa 4"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:47.1"
msgid "若比丘尼有漏心。從漏心男子自手取食。是法初犯僧伽婆尸沙可沙可悔過。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="ss5" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:48.1"
msgid "saṅghadisesa 5"
msgstr "saṅghadisesa 5"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="15"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:49.1"
msgid "若比丘尼語比丘尼言。若汝無漏心。從漏心男子自手取食噉。若隨意用。於汝何所能。是法初犯僧伽婆尸沙可沙可悔過。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="ss6" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:50.1"
msgid "saṅghadisesa 6"
msgstr "saṅghadisesa 6"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:51.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。若夜若晝。若異聚落若異界。若度水彼岸一身獨宿。是法初犯僧伽婆尸沙可沙可悔過。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="ss7" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:52.1"
msgid "saṅghadisesa 7"
msgstr "saṅghadisesa 7"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:53.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。恃勢言人者。是法初犯僧伽婆尸沙可沙可悔過。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="ss8" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:54.1"
msgid "saṅghadisesa 8"
msgstr "saṅghadisesa 8"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:55.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。知賊女決斷應死。眾人皆知王及主不聽。便作弟子。是法初犯僧伽婆尸沙可沙可悔過。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="ss9" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:56.1"
msgid "saṅghadisesa 9"
msgstr "saṅghadisesa 9"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="16"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:57.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。知比丘尼和合僧如法作不見擯。不問比丘尼僧亦不取欲。便出界外與解擯者。是法初犯僧伽婆尸沙可沙可悔過。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="ss10" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:58.1"
msgid "saṅghadisesa 10"
msgstr "saṅghadisesa 10"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="17"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:59.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。欲破和合僧。懃方便受持破僧事。諸比丘尼應如是諫。汝莫破和合僧懃方便受持破僧事。當與僧和合。僧和合者歡喜無諍。一心一學如水乳合。得安樂住。汝當捨是求破僧事。諸比丘尼如是諫時。堅持是事不捨者。當再三諫令捨是事。再三諫時捨者善。不捨者是法至三。犯僧伽婆尸沙可沙可悔過。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="ss11" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:60.1"
msgid "saṅghadisesa 11"
msgstr "saṅghadisesa 11"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="18"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:61.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。求破和合僧。有餘同意相助比丘尼。若一若二若多。語諸比丘尼言。汝是事中莫說是比丘尼。何以故。是比丘尼說法說律。不說非法。不說非律。是比丘尼所說。皆是我等所欲。是知說非不知說。是比丘尼所說。皆是我等所欲樂忍。諸比丘尼應如是諫是相助比丘尼。汝莫作是語。是比丘尼說法說律。不說非法不說非律。是比丘尼所說。皆是我等所欲。是知說非不知說。是比丘尼所說。皆是我等所欲樂忍。汝莫相助求破僧事。當助和合僧。僧和合者歡喜無諍。一心一學如水乳合。得安樂住。諸比丘尼如是諫時。堅持是事不捨者。諸比丘尼當再三諫。令捨是事故。再三諫時捨者善。不捨者是法至三。犯僧伽婆尸沙可沙可悔過。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="ss12" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:62.1"
msgid "saṅghadisesa 12"
msgstr "saṅghadisesa 12"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="19"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:63.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。隨所依止聚落。作惡行污他家。皆見皆聞皆知。諸比丘尼應如是言。汝等作惡行污他家。皆見皆聞皆知。汝等出去。不應住此。是比丘尼語諸比丘尼言。諸比丘尼。隨愛隨瞋隨怖隨癡行。何以故。有如是同罪比丘尼。有驅者有不驅者。諸比丘尼語是比丘尼。汝莫作是語。諸比丘尼隨愛隨瞋隨怖隨癡行。何以故。諸比丘尼不隨愛瞋怖癡行。汝等作惡行污他家。皆見聞知。汝當捨是隨愛瞋怖癡語。汝等出去。不應住此。如是諫時不捨是事者。當再三諫。令捨是事故。再三諫時捨者善。不捨者。僧伽婆尸沙可沙可悔過。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="ss13" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:64.1"
msgid "saṅghadisesa 13"
msgstr "saṅghadisesa 13"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="20"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:65.1"
msgid "有比丘尼惡性戾語。諸比丘尼。說如法如律如戒經中事。是比丘尼戾語不受。語諸比丘尼言。汝莫語我好惡。我亦不語汝好惡。諸比丘尼應如是言。諸比丘尼。說如法如律如戒經中事。汝莫戾語當隨順語。諸比丘尼。當為汝說如法如律。汝亦當為諸比丘尼說如法如律。何以故。如是者。諸如來眾得增長利益。以共語相教共罪中出故。汝當捨是戾語事。諸比丘尼如是諫時。堅持是事不捨者。諸比丘尼當再三諫。令捨是事故再三諫時捨者善。不捨者僧伽婆尸沙可沙可悔過。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="ss14" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:66.1"
msgid "saṅghadisesa 14"
msgstr "saṅghadisesa 14"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="21"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:67.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。共比丘尼<span class=\"gaiji\">鬪<!--gaiji,鬥,1[鬥@(豆*寸)],2&#x9B2A;,3--> </span>諍時。作是言。我捨佛捨法捨僧捨戒。非但沙門釋子知道。更有餘沙門婆羅門。有慚愧善好樂持戒者。我當從彼修梵行。諸比丘尼應諫是比丘尼言。汝莫共諸比丘尼<span class=\"gaiji\">鬪<!--gaiji,鬥,1[鬥@(豆*寸)],2&#x9B2A;,3--> </span>諍時作是言。我捨佛捨法捨僧捨戒。非但沙門釋子知道。更有餘沙門婆羅門。有慚愧善好樂持戒者。我當從彼修梵行。汝應佛法中樂修梵行。當捨離自不樂心。諸比丘尼如是諫時。堅持是事不捨者。當再三諫。令捨是事故。再三諫時捨者善。不捨者僧伽婆尸沙可沙可悔過。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="ss15" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:68.1"
msgid "saṅghadisesa 15"
msgstr "saṅghadisesa 15"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="22"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:69.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。共比丘尼<span class=\"gaiji\">鬪<!--gaiji,鬥,1[鬥@(豆*寸)],2&#x9B2A;,3--> </span>諍時。作是言。比丘尼僧。隨愛行隨瞋行隨怖行隨癡行。諸比丘尼應如是諫。汝莫共諸比丘尼<span class=\"gaiji\">鬪<!--gaiji,鬥,1[鬥@(豆*寸)],2&#x9B2A;,3--> </span>諍時作是言。比丘尼僧。隨愛行隨瞋行隨怖行隨癡行。何以故。比丘尼僧。不隨愛瞋怖癡行。汝當捨是隨愛瞋怖癡語。諸比丘尼如是諫時。堅持是事不捨者。諸比丘尼應再三諫。令捨是事故。再三諫時捨者善。不捨者僧伽婆尸沙可沙可悔過。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="ss16" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:70.1"
msgid "saṅghadisesa 16"
msgstr "saṅghadisesa 16"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="23"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:71.1"
msgid "若二比丘尼同心共作惡業。有惡名聲。惱比丘尼僧。互相覆罪。諸比丘尼應如是諫。汝等莫同心共作惡業有惡名聲。惱比丘尼僧。互相覆罪。汝等各別離行。別離行者增長佛法。汝等捨是隨順惡行。諸比丘尼如是諫時。堅持是事不捨者。應再三諫。令捨是事故。再三諫時捨者善。不捨者僧伽婆尸沙可沙可悔過。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="ss17" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:72.1"
msgid "saṅghadisesa 17"
msgstr "saṅghadisesa 17"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="24"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:73.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。教二比丘尼言。汝莫別離行。當同心行。別離行者不得增長。若同心行者便得增長。比丘尼僧中。亦有如汝等者。僧以瞋故。教汝別離行。諸比丘尼應如是諫。汝莫教二比丘尼作是言。汝等莫別離行。當同心行。別離行者不得增長佛法。同心行者便得增長。眾中亦有如汝等者。僧以瞋故。教汝別離行。汝當捨是勸邪行事。諸比丘尼如是諫時。堅持是事不捨者。當再三諫。令捨是事故。再三諫時捨者善。不捨者僧伽婆尸沙可沙可悔過。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="25"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:74.1"
msgid "諸大德。已說十七僧伽婆尸沙法。九初罪八乃至三諫。若比丘尼隨犯一一罪。應二部僧中半月行摩那埵。可二部僧意。二部僧各二十眾。應出是比丘尼罪。若二部眾中若少一人。是比丘尼罪不名為出。二部僧可呵。是法應爾。今問諸大德。是中清淨不。第二第三亦如是問。是中清淨不。諸大德。是中清淨。默然故。是事如是持。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h2>
#. <span class="add"><a id="np" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:75.1"
msgid "30 nissaggiya pācittiya rules"
msgstr "30 nissaggiya pācittiya rules"

#. </a></span>
#. </h2><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:76.1"
msgid "諸大德。是三十尼薩耆波夜提法。半月半月波羅提木叉中說。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="np1" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:77.1"
msgid "nissaggiya pācittiya 1"
msgstr "nissaggiya pācittiya 1"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:78.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。衣竟已捨迦絺那衣。畜長衣得至十日。過是畜者。尼薩耆波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="np2" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:79.1"
msgid "nissaggiya pācittiya 2"
msgstr "nissaggiya pācittiya 2"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:80.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。衣竟已捨迦絺那衣。五衣中若離一一衣。乃至一宿。尼薩耆波夜提。除僧羯磨。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="np3" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:81.1"
msgid "nissaggiya pācittiya 3"
msgstr "nissaggiya pācittiya 3"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="26"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:82.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。衣竟已捨迦絺那衣。若得非時衣。是比丘尼須者當自手取。速作受持。若足者善。若不足者。更望得衣令具足故。停是衣乃至一月。過是停者。尼薩耆波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="np4" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:83.1"
msgid "nissaggiya pācittiya 4"
msgstr "nissaggiya pācittiya 4"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:84.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。從非親里居士居士婦乞衣。得衣者。尼薩耆波夜提。除因緣。因緣者。奪衣失衣燒衣漂衣。是名因緣。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="np5" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:85.1"
msgid "nissaggiya pācittiya 5"
msgstr "nissaggiya pācittiya 5"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="27"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:86.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。奪衣失衣燒衣漂衣時。從非親里居士居士婦乞衣。自恣多與衣。是比丘尼應取上下衣。過是取者。尼薩耆波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="np6" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:87.1"
msgid "nissaggiya pācittiya 6"
msgstr "nissaggiya pācittiya 6"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="28"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:88.1"
msgid "若為比丘尼故。非親里居士居士婦辦衣直作是言。我以是衣直。買如是衣。與某比丘尼。是比丘尼。先不自恣請。便往居士居士婦所。作同意言。汝為我辦如是衣直。買如是如是衣與我。為好故。若得衣者。尼薩耆波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="np7" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:89.1"
msgid "nissaggiya pācittiya 7"
msgstr "nissaggiya pācittiya 7"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="29"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:90.1"
msgid "若為比丘尼。二非親里居士居士婦。各辦衣直作是言。我以是衣直。各買如是衣。與某比丘尼。是比丘尼。先不自恣請。便往居士居士婦所。作同意言。汝等各辦衣直。合作一衣與我。為好故。若得衣者。尼薩耆波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="np8" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:91.1"
msgid "nissaggiya pācittiya 8"
msgstr "nissaggiya pācittiya 8"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="30"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:92.1"
msgid "若為比丘尼故。若王王臣若婆羅門居士。遣使送衣直。是使到比丘尼所言。大德。某送此衣直。汝當受取。比丘尼應言。我比丘尼法。不應受衣直。若須衣時得淨衣者。當自手受速作衣持使語比丘尼言。大德。有執事人。能為比丘尼執事不。是比丘尼應示執事人。若僧園民若優婆塞。此人能為比丘尼執事。是使往執事人所言。汝取是衣直。作如是衣。與某比丘尼。是比丘尼須衣時來。汝當與衣。是使語已還報比丘尼。我已語竟。大德。須衣時便往取。當與汝衣。是比丘尼往執事所索衣。作是言。我須衣。至再三反亦如是索。得衣者善。不得者四反乃至六反。往執事人前默然立。若四反乃至六反默然立。得衣者善。若不得衣。過是求得衣者。尼薩耆波夜提。若不得衣。隨送衣直來處。若自往若遣使語。汝所送衣直。我不得。汝自知物莫使失。是事應爾。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="np9" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:93.1"
msgid "nissaggiya pācittiya 9"
msgstr "nissaggiya pācittiya 9"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:94.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。自手取寶。若使人取。尼薩耆波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="np10" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:95.1"
msgid "nissaggiya pācittiya 10"
msgstr "nissaggiya pācittiya 10"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:96.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。種種用寶者。尼薩耆波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="np11" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:97.1"
msgid "nissaggiya pācittiya 11"
msgstr "nissaggiya pācittiya 11"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:98.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。種種販賣者。尼薩耆波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="np12" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:99.1"
msgid "nissaggiya pācittiya 12"
msgstr "nissaggiya pācittiya 12"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="31"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:100.1"
msgid "若比丘尼所用<span class=\"gaiji\">鉢<!--gaiji,缽,1[金*本],2&#x9262;,3--> </span>破減五綴。更乞新<span class=\"gaiji\">鉢<!--gaiji,缽,1[金*本],2&#x9262;,3--> </span>。為好故。尼薩耆波夜提。是<span class=\"gaiji\">鉢<!--gaiji,缽,1[金*本],2&#x9262;,3--> </span>應比丘尼僧中捨。眾中最下<span class=\"gaiji\">鉢<!--gaiji,缽,1[金*本],2&#x9262;,3--> </span>。應與是比丘尼。如是教言。汝比丘尼畜是<span class=\"gaiji\">鉢<!--gaiji,缽,1[金*本],2&#x9262;,3--> </span>。乃至破。是事應爾。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="np13" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:101.1"
msgid "nissaggiya pācittiya 13"
msgstr "nissaggiya pācittiya 13"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:102.1"
msgid "若比丘尼自乞縷。使非親里織師織。尼薩耆波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="np14" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:103.1"
msgid "nissaggiya pācittiya 14"
msgstr "nissaggiya pācittiya 14"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="32"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:104.1"
msgid "若為比丘尼故。非親里居士居士婦。使織師為織衣。是比丘尼先不請。便往語織師言。汝知不。是衣為我故織。汝好織極好織廣織淨潔織。我當多少益汝。是比丘尼。若自語若使人語。後時若與食。若與食直。為好故。得衣者。尼薩耆波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="np15" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:105.1"
msgid "nissaggiya pācittiya 15"
msgstr "nissaggiya pācittiya 15"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:106.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。與比丘尼衣。後瞋恚嫌恨。若自奪若使人奪。還我衣來不與汝。得衣者。尼薩耆波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="np16" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:107.1"
msgid "nissaggiya pācittiya 16"
msgstr "nissaggiya pācittiya 16"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:108.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。十日未至自恣。有急施衣應受。比丘尼須是衣者。當自手取乃至衣時畜。過是畜者。尼薩耆波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="np17" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:109.1"
msgid "nissaggiya pācittiya 17"
msgstr "nissaggiya pācittiya 17"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:110.1"
msgid "若比丘尼知物向僧。自求向己者。尼薩耆波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="np18" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:111.1"
msgid "nissaggiya pācittiya 18"
msgstr "nissaggiya pācittiya 18"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:112.1"
msgid "若比丘尼病。聽服四種含消藥。酥油蜜石蜜。共宿至七日得服。過是服者。尼薩耆波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="np19" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:113.1"
msgid "nissaggiya pācittiya 19"
msgstr "nissaggiya pācittiya 19"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:114.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。畜長<span class=\"gaiji\">鉢<!--gaiji,缽,1[金*本],2&#x9262;,3--> </span>乃至一夜。過是畜者。尼薩耆波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="np20" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:115.1"
msgid "nissaggiya pācittiya 20"
msgstr "nissaggiya pācittiya 20"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:116.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。時衣作非時衣分者。尼薩耆波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="np21" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:117.1"
msgid "nissaggiya pācittiya 21"
msgstr "nissaggiya pācittiya 21"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:118.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。非時衣作時衣分者。尼薩耆波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="np22" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:119.1"
msgid "nissaggiya pācittiya 22"
msgstr "nissaggiya pācittiya 22"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:120.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。共比丘尼貿衣。後到比丘尼所。作是言。我還汝衣。汝還我衣。得衣者。尼薩耆波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="np23" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:121.1"
msgid "nissaggiya pācittiya 23"
msgstr "nissaggiya pācittiya 23"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="33"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:122.1"
msgid "若為比丘尼故。眾多非親里居士居士婦。各各辦衣直作是言。我等以是衣直。各買如是衣。與某比丘尼。是比丘尼先不請。後到眾多居士居士婦所。作是言。汝等以是衣直。共買如是一衣與我。為好故。得是衣者。尼薩耆波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="np24" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:123.1"
msgid "nissaggiya pācittiya 24"
msgstr "nissaggiya pācittiya 24"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:124.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。自為乞金銀。尼薩耆波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="np25" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:125.1"
msgid "nissaggiya pācittiya 25"
msgstr "nissaggiya pācittiya 25"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:126.1"
msgid "若比丘尼乞是已。更索餘者。尼薩耆波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="np26" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:127.1"
msgid "nissaggiya pācittiya 26"
msgstr "nissaggiya pācittiya 26"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:128.1"
msgid "若比丘尼為僧是事乞。作餘事用。尼薩耆波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="np27" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:129.1"
msgid "nissaggiya pācittiya 27"
msgstr "nissaggiya pācittiya 27"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:130.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。自為是事乞。作餘事用。尼薩耆波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="np28" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:131.1"
msgid "nissaggiya pācittiya 28"
msgstr "nissaggiya pācittiya 28"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:132.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。為多人是事乞。作餘事用。尼薩耆波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="np29" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:133.1"
msgid "nissaggiya pācittiya 29"
msgstr "nissaggiya pācittiya 29"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:134.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。乞重衣。應乞四錢直衣。過是乞。尼薩耆波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="np30" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:135.1"
msgid "nissaggiya pācittiya 30"
msgstr "nissaggiya pācittiya 30"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:136.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。乞輕衣。應乞二錢半直衣。過是乞。尼薩耆波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="34"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:137.1"
msgid "諸大德。已說三十尼薩耆波夜提法。今問諸大德。是中清淨不。第二第三亦如是問。是中清淨不。諸大德。是中清淨。默然故。是事如是持。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h2>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:138.1"
msgid "108 pācittiya rules"
msgstr "108 pācittiya rules"

#. </a></span>
#. </h2><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:139.1"
msgid "諸大德是百七十八波夜提法。半月半月波羅提木叉中說。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc1" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:140.1"
msgid "pācittiya 1"
msgstr "pācittiya 1"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:141.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。故妄語。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc2" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:142.1"
msgid "pācittiya 2"
msgstr "pācittiya 2"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:143.1"
msgid "若比丘尼形相比丘尼。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc3" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:144.1"
msgid "pācittiya 3"
msgstr "pācittiya 3"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:145.1"
msgid "若比丘尼兩舌者。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc4" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:146.1"
msgid "pācittiya 4"
msgstr "pācittiya 4"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:147.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。僧如法斷諍竟。還更發起。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc5" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:148.1"
msgid "pācittiya 5"
msgstr "pācittiya 5"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:149.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。以句法教未受具戒人者。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc6" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:150.1"
msgid "pācittiya 6"
msgstr "pācittiya 6"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:151.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。實有過人法。向未受具戒人說。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc7" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:152.1"
msgid "pācittiya 7"
msgstr "pācittiya 7"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:153.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。知比丘尼有惡罪。向未受具戒人說波夜提。除僧羯磨。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc8" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:154.1"
msgid "pācittiya 8"
msgstr "pācittiya 8"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:155.1"
msgid "若比丘尼先自勸與。後作是言。諸比丘尼。隨親厚迴僧物與。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc9" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:156.1"
msgid "pācittiya 9"
msgstr "pācittiya 9"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="35"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:157.1"
msgid "若比丘尼說戒時。作是言。何用是雜碎戒為。半月說時。令諸比丘尼疑悔惱熱愁憂不樂生反戒心。作是輕呵戒者。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc10" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:158.1"
msgid "pācittiya 10"
msgstr "pācittiya 10"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:159.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。斫伐鬼村種子村。波夜提<span class=\"counter\">(一十)</span>。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h3>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:160.1"
msgid "<span class=\"add latin\">Chapter 1</span>"
msgstr ""

#. </h3><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc11" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:161.1"
msgid "pācittiya 11"
msgstr "pācittiya 11"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:162.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。瞋譏僧所差人。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc12" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:163.1"
msgid "pācittiya 12"
msgstr "pācittiya 12"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:164.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。用異事默然惱他。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc13" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:165.1"
msgid "pācittiya 13"
msgstr "pācittiya 13"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:166.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。露地敷僧臥具。<span class=\"gaiji\">麁<!--gaiji,麤,1[色-巴+鹿],2&#x9E81;,3--> </span>細繩床被褥若使人敷是中坐臥。去時不自舉不教人舉。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc14" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:167.1"
msgid "pācittiya 14"
msgstr "pācittiya 14"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:168.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。比丘尼房中敷僧臥具。若使人敷。是中坐臥。去時不自舉不教人舉。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc15" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:169.1"
msgid "pācittiya 15"
msgstr "pācittiya 15"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:170.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。比丘尼房中瞋恨不喜。便自牽出。若使人牽。癡人遠去。不應住此。波夜提。除因緣。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc16" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:171.1"
msgid "pācittiya 16"
msgstr "pācittiya 16"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:172.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。比丘尼房中知他先敷臥具。後來強敷若使人敷。不樂者自當出去。波夜提。除因緣。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc17" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:173.1"
msgid "pācittiya 17"
msgstr "pācittiya 17"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:174.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。比丘尼房閣中。尖<span class=\"gaiji\">脚<!--gaiji,腳,1[腳-谷+去],2&#x811A;,3--> </span>坐床若臥床。用力坐臥。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc18" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:175.1"
msgid "pācittiya 18"
msgstr "pācittiya 18"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:176.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。知水有蟲。自用澆草和泥。若使人用。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc19" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:177.1"
msgid "pācittiya 19"
msgstr "pācittiya 19"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:178.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。獨與一比丘屏覆處坐。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc20" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:179.1"
msgid "pācittiya 20"
msgstr "pācittiya 20"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:180.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。不病住福德舍。過一食者。波夜提<span class=\"counter\">(二十)</span>。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h3>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:181.1"
msgid "<span class=\"add latin\">Chapter 2</span>"
msgstr ""

#. </h3><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc21" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:182.1"
msgid "pācittiya 21"
msgstr "pācittiya 21"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="36"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:183.1"
msgid "若比丘尼往白衣家。自恣請多與餅<span class=\"gaiji\">麨<!--gaiji,,1[麩-夫+少],2&#x9EA8;,3--> </span>。諸比丘尼須者。應二三<span class=\"gaiji\">鉢<!--gaiji,缽,1[金*本],2&#x9262;,3--> </span>取。過是取者。波夜提。二三<span class=\"gaiji\">鉢<!--gaiji,缽,1[金*本],2&#x9262;,3--> </span>取已出外。與餘比丘尼共分。是法應爾。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc22" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:184.1"
msgid "pācittiya 22"
msgstr "pācittiya 22"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:185.1"
msgid "若比丘尼別眾食。波夜提。除因緣。因緣者。病時作衣時道行時船行時大眾集時沙門請時。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc23" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:186.1"
msgid "pācittiya 23"
msgstr "pācittiya 23"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:187.1"
msgid "若比丘尼非時噉食。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc24" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:188.1"
msgid "pācittiya 24"
msgstr "pācittiya 24"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:189.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。舉殘宿食食者。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc25" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:190.1"
msgid "pācittiya 25"
msgstr "pācittiya 25"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:191.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。不受食著口中。波夜提。除水及楊枝。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc26" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:192.1"
msgid "pācittiya 26"
msgstr "pācittiya 26"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:193.1"
msgid "若比丘尼知水有蟲取用。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc27" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:194.1"
msgid "pācittiya 27"
msgstr "pācittiya 27"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:195.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。有食家中強坐。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc28" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:196.1"
msgid "pācittiya 28"
msgstr "pācittiya 28"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:197.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。食家中獨與一男子舍內強坐。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc29" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:198.1"
msgid "pācittiya 29"
msgstr "pācittiya 29"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:199.1"
msgid "若比丘尼裸形外道。若出家男出家女。自手與食。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc30" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:200.1"
msgid "pācittiya 30"
msgstr "pācittiya 30"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:201.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。故往看軍發行。波夜提除因緣<span class=\"counter\">(三十)</span>。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h3>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:202.1"
msgid "<span class=\"add latin\">Chapter 3</span>"
msgstr ""

#. </h3><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc31" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:203.1"
msgid "pācittiya 31"
msgstr "pācittiya 31"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:204.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。有因緣往軍中宿。過二夜。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc32" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:205.1"
msgid "pācittiya 32"
msgstr "pācittiya 32"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:206.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。二夜軍中宿時。往看軍陣器仗牙旗幡幢兩陣合戰。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc33" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:207.1"
msgid "pācittiya 33"
msgstr "pācittiya 33"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:208.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。瞋打比丘尼。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc34" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:209.1"
msgid "pācittiya 34"
msgstr "pācittiya 34"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:210.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。瞋舉手向比丘尼。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc35" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:211.1"
msgid "pācittiya 35"
msgstr "pācittiya 35"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:212.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。知比丘尼犯僧殘罪。覆藏乃至一夜。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc36" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:213.1"
msgid "pācittiya 36"
msgstr "pācittiya 36"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="37"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:214.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。語餘比丘尼。來共到諸家。是比丘尼不教與食。便作是言。汝去。與汝共坐共語不樂。我獨坐獨語樂。欲惱彼故。以是因緣無異。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc37" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:215.1"
msgid "pācittiya 37"
msgstr "pācittiya 37"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:216.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。無病露地燃火。若草木牛糞木皮糞掃。若自燃若使人燃。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc38" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:217.1"
msgid "pācittiya 38"
msgstr "pācittiya 38"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:218.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。如法僧事與欲竟。後悔言。我不應與。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc39" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:219.1"
msgid "pācittiya 39"
msgstr "pācittiya 39"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:220.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。與未受具戒人同室宿。過二夜。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc40" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:221.1"
msgid "pācittiya 40"
msgstr "pācittiya 40"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="38"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:222.1"
msgid "若比丘尼作是語。我如是知佛法義。行障道法不能障道。諸比丘尼應如是諫。汝莫作是語。我知佛法義。行障道法不能障道。汝莫謗佛。謗佛者不善。佛不作是語。佛種種因緣說障道法能障道。汝當捨是惡邪見。諸比丘尼如是諫時。堅持不捨者。當再三諫令捨是事。再三諫時捨者善。不捨者波夜提<span class=\"counter\">(四十)</span>。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h3>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:223.1"
msgid "<span class=\"add latin\">Chapter 4</span>"
msgstr ""

#. </h3><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc41" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:224.1"
msgid "pācittiya 41"
msgstr "pācittiya 41"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:225.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。知比丘尼作如是語。不如法悔不捨惡邪如法擯出。便與共事共住共同室宿波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc42" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:226.1"
msgid "pācittiya 42"
msgstr "pācittiya 42"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="39"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:227.1"
msgid "若有沙彌尼作是語。我知佛法義。行婬欲不能障道。諸比丘尼應如是教言。汝莫作是語。我知佛法義。行婬欲不能障道。汝莫謗佛。謗佛者不善。佛不作是語。佛種種因緣說婬欲能障道法。汝當捨是惡邪見。諸比丘尼如是教時。堅持是事不捨者。當再三教令捨是事。再三教時捨者善。不捨者。諸比丘尼應如是語。汝沙彌尼。從今不應言佛是我師。亦不應隨諸比丘尼後行。餘沙彌尼。得共比丘尼同房再宿。汝今不得。癡人滅去。不應住此。若比丘尼。知是滅擯沙彌尼。便畜經恤共事共宿。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc43" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:228.1"
msgid "pācittiya 43"
msgstr "pācittiya 43"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="40"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:229.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。若寶似寶。自捉教人捉。波夜提。除因緣。因緣者。若寶似寶。在僧坊內若住處內如是心取。主來當還。是事應爾。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc44" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:230.1"
msgid "pācittiya 44"
msgstr "pācittiya 44"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="41"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:231.1"
msgid "若比丘尼得新衣。應三種色中隨用一一種。壞是衣色。若青若泥若木蘭。若比丘尼。不以三種壞色著新衣。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc45" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:232.1"
msgid "pācittiya 45"
msgstr "pācittiya 45"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="42"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:233.1"
msgid "若比丘尼減半月浴。波夜提。除因緣。因緣者。春殘一月半。夏初一月。是二月半。大熱時病時風時雨時作時行時。是名因緣。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc46" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:234.1"
msgid "pācittiya 46"
msgstr "pācittiya 46"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:235.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。故奪畜生命。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc47" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:236.1"
msgid "pācittiya 47"
msgstr "pācittiya 47"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:237.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。故令比丘尼疑悔。使須臾時心不安隱。以是因緣無異。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc48" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:238.1"
msgid "pācittiya 48"
msgstr "pācittiya 48"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:239.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。以指擊<span class=\"gaiji\">攊<!--gaiji,擽,1[打-丁+歷],2&#x650A;,3--> </span>他。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc49" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:240.1"
msgid "pācittiya 49"
msgstr "pācittiya 49"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:241.1"
msgid "若比丘尼水中戲。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc50" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:242.1"
msgid "pācittiya 50"
msgstr "pācittiya 50"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:243.1"
msgid "若比丘尼與男子同室宿。波夜提<span class=\"counter\">(五十)</span>。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h3>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:244.1"
msgid "<span class=\"add latin\">Chapter 5</span>"
msgstr ""

#. </h3><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc51" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:245.1"
msgid "pācittiya 51"
msgstr "pācittiya 51"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:246.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。自恐怖比丘尼。若使他恐怖。乃至戲笑。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc52" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:247.1"
msgid "pācittiya 52"
msgstr "pācittiya 52"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:248.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。自藏比丘尼衣<span class=\"gaiji\">鉢<!--gaiji,缽,1[金*本],2&#x9262;,3--> </span>戶鉤革屣鍼筒。種種隨法物。若使他藏。乃至戲笑。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc53" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:249.1"
msgid "pācittiya 53"
msgstr "pācittiya 53"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:250.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。與比丘比丘尼式叉摩尼沙彌沙彌尼衣。他不還便強脫取。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc54" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:251.1"
msgid "pācittiya 54"
msgstr "pācittiya 54"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:252.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。以無根僧伽婆尸沙法。謗比丘尼。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc55" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:253.1"
msgid "pācittiya 55"
msgstr "pācittiya 55"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:254.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。與男子共期同道行。至一聚落。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc56" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:255.1"
msgid "pācittiya 56"
msgstr "pācittiya 56"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:256.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。與賊共期同道行。乃至一聚落。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc57" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:257.1"
msgid "pācittiya 57"
msgstr "pācittiya 57"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:258.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。自手掘地。若教他掘。作是言。汝掘是處。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc58" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:259.1"
msgid "pācittiya 58"
msgstr "pācittiya 58"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:260.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。受四月自恣請。過是受者。波夜提。除常請數數請別請。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc59" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:261.1"
msgid "pācittiya 59"
msgstr "pācittiya 59"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:262.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。說戒時作是言。我不受學是戒。先當問餘比丘持修多羅持毘尼持摩多羅伽者。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc60" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:263.1"
msgid "pācittiya 60"
msgstr "pācittiya 60"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="43"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:264.1"
msgid "若比丘尼欲知是法者。應從此戒中學。當問餘比丘。持修多羅持毘尼持摩多羅伽者。應如是問。是語云何。是事應爾。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:265.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。共比丘尼<span class=\"gaiji\">鬪<!--gaiji,鬥,1[鬥@(豆*寸)],2&#x9B2A;,3--> </span>諍已。盜往立聽。彼比丘尼所說我當憶持。波夜提<span class=\"counter\">(六十)</span>。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h3>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:266.1"
msgid "<span class=\"add latin\">Chapter 6</span>"
msgstr ""

#. </h3><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc61" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:267.1"
msgid "pācittiya 61"
msgstr "pācittiya 61"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:268.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。僧斷事時默然起去。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc62" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:269.1"
msgid "pācittiya 62"
msgstr "pācittiya 62"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:270.1"
msgid "若比丘尼不恭敬者。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc63" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:271.1"
msgid "pācittiya 63"
msgstr "pācittiya 63"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:272.1"
msgid "若比丘尼飲酒者。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc64" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:273.1"
msgid "pācittiya 64"
msgstr "pācittiya 64"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:274.1"
msgid "若比丘尼非時入聚落。不白餘比丘尼。波夜提。除急因緣。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc65" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:275.1"
msgid "pācittiya 65"
msgstr "pācittiya 65"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:276.1"
msgid "若比丘尼許他請僧。中前中後行至餘家。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc66" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:277.1"
msgid "pācittiya 66"
msgstr "pācittiya 66"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:278.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。入灌頂剎利王家。夜未過未藏寶。若過門闑及闑處。波夜提。除急因緣。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc67" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:279.1"
msgid "pācittiya 67"
msgstr "pācittiya 67"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="44"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:280.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。說戒時作是言。我今始知是事入戒經中半月次來所說。諸比丘尼知是比丘尼先曾再三聞說此戒。何況復過。是比丘尼非以不知故得脫。隨所犯事應令如法悔過。應呵令厭汝失無利是惡不善。汝說戒時不尊重戒不一心聽。以是事故。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc68" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:281.1"
msgid "pācittiya 68"
msgstr "pācittiya 68"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:282.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。用骨牙齒角作鍼筒。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc69" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:283.1"
msgid "pācittiya 69"
msgstr "pācittiya 69"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:284.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。欲作床者。當應量作。足高八指。除入梐。過是作者。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc70" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:285.1"
msgid "pācittiya 70"
msgstr "pācittiya 70"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:286.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。自以兜羅貯臥具。若使人貯。波夜提<span class=\"counter\">(七十)</span>。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h3>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:287.1"
msgid "<span class=\"add latin\">Chapter 7</span>"
msgstr ""

#. </h3><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc71" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:288.1"
msgid "pācittiya 71"
msgstr "pācittiya 71"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:289.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。如佛衣量作衣。若過作。波夜提。佛衣量者。長佛九磔手。廣六磔手。是佛衣量。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc72" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:290.1"
msgid "pācittiya 72"
msgstr "pācittiya 72"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:291.1"
msgid "若比丘尼噉生熟蒜。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc73" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:292.1"
msgid "pācittiya 73"
msgstr "pācittiya 73"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:293.1"
msgid "若比丘尼剃大小便處毛。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc74" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:294.1"
msgid "pācittiya 74"
msgstr "pācittiya 74"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:295.1"
msgid "若比丘尼洗時以指刺女根中。過二指節。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc75" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:296.1"
msgid "pācittiya 75"
msgstr "pācittiya 75"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:297.1"
msgid "若比丘尼以掌拍女根者。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc76" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:298.1"
msgid "pācittiya 76"
msgstr "pācittiya 76"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:299.1"
msgid "若比丘尼煮生物作食。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc77" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:300.1"
msgid "pācittiya 77"
msgstr "pācittiya 77"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:301.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。比丘食時在前立待。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc78" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:302.1"
msgid "pācittiya 78"
msgstr "pācittiya 78"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:303.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。以屎尿擲牆外。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc79" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:304.1"
msgid "pācittiya 79"
msgstr "pācittiya 79"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:305.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。棄屎尿著生草上。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc80" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:306.1"
msgid "pācittiya 80"
msgstr "pācittiya 80"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:307.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。獨與一比丘屏處共立共語。波夜提<span class=\"counter\">(八十)</span>。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h3>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:308.1"
msgid "<span class=\"add latin\">Chapter 8</span>"
msgstr ""

#. </h3><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc81" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:309.1"
msgid "pācittiya 81"
msgstr "pācittiya 81"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:310.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。獨與一比丘露地共立共語。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc82" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:311.1"
msgid "pācittiya 82"
msgstr "pācittiya 82"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:312.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。獨與一白衣男子屏處共立共語。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc83" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:313.1"
msgid "pācittiya 83"
msgstr "pācittiya 83"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:314.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。獨與一白衣男子露地共立共語。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc84" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:315.1"
msgid "pācittiya 84"
msgstr "pācittiya 84"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:316.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。闇中無燈與男子共立共坐。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc85" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:317.1"
msgid "pācittiya 85"
msgstr "pācittiya 85"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:318.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。作男根著女根中。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc86" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:319.1"
msgid "pācittiya 86"
msgstr "pācittiya 86"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p><a class="sc" id="45"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:320.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。語比丘尼言。善女來。共我房住。後瞋不喜。若自牽出。若使人牽出。作是言。汝遠滅去。莫此中住。以是因緣無異。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc87" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:321.1"
msgid "pācittiya 87"
msgstr "pācittiya 87"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:322.1"
msgid "若二比丘尼共一床臥。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc88" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:323.1"
msgid "pācittiya 88"
msgstr "pācittiya 88"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:324.1"
msgid "若二比丘尼共一敷具臥。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc89" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:325.1"
msgid "pācittiya 89"
msgstr "pācittiya 89"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:326.1"
msgid "若二比丘尼共一衣覆臥。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc90" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:327.1"
msgid "pācittiya 90"
msgstr "pācittiya 90"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:328.1"
msgid "若比丘尼入白衣舍。獨與一比丘共立共語竊語。遣共行比丘尼求閑便故。波夜提<span class=\"counter\">(九十)</span>。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h3>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:329.1"
msgid "<span class=\"add latin\">Chapter 9</span>"
msgstr ""

#. </h3><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc91" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:330.1"
msgid "pācittiya 91"
msgstr "pācittiya 91"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:331.1"
msgid "若比丘尼入白衣舍。獨與一白衣男子共立共語竊語。遣共行比丘尼。欲獨語。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc92" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:332.1"
msgid "pācittiya 92"
msgstr "pācittiya 92"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:333.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。共比丘尼<span class=\"gaiji\">鬪<!--gaiji,鬥,1[鬥@(豆*寸)],2&#x9B2A;,3--> </span>諍相瞋。自打身啼者。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc93" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:334.1"
msgid "pācittiya 93"
msgstr "pācittiya 93"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:335.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。共比丘尼<span class=\"gaiji\">鬪<!--gaiji,鬥,1[鬥@(豆*寸)],2&#x9B2A;,3--> </span>諍時。作法<span class=\"gaiji\">呪<!--gaiji,咒,1[口*兄],2&#x546A;,3--> </span>泥梨<span class=\"gaiji\">呪<!--gaiji,咒,1[口*兄],2&#x546A;,3--> </span>。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc94" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:336.1"
msgid "pācittiya 94"
msgstr "pācittiya 94"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:337.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。不審諦看物便嫌恨。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc95" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:338.1"
msgid "pācittiya 95"
msgstr "pācittiya 95"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:339.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。夏中無因緣遊行他國。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc96" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:340.1"
msgid "pācittiya 96"
msgstr "pācittiya 96"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:341.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。自恣竟不遊行餘處一宿。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc97" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:342.1"
msgid "pācittiya 97"
msgstr "pācittiya 97"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:343.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。國內疑處畏處遊行。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc98" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:344.1"
msgid "pācittiya 98"
msgstr "pācittiya 98"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:345.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。國外疑處畏處遊行。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc99" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:346.1"
msgid "pācittiya 99"
msgstr "pācittiya 99"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:347.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。故<span class=\"choice\"><span class=\"sic\">徃</span><span class=\"corr\">往</span></span>看畫舍。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc100" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:348.1"
msgid "pācittiya 100"
msgstr "pācittiya 100"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:349.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。先住惱後住者。波夜提<span class=\"counter\">(一百)</span>。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h3>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:350.1"
msgid "<span class=\"add latin\">Chapter 10</span>"
msgstr ""

#. </h3><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc101" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:351.1"
msgid "pācittiya 101"
msgstr "pācittiya 101"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:352.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。後住惱先住者。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc102" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:353.1"
msgid "pācittiya 102"
msgstr "pācittiya 102"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:354.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。共活比丘尼病不供給。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc103" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:355.1"
msgid "pācittiya 103"
msgstr "pācittiya 103"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:356.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。見比丘來不起。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc104" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:357.1"
msgid "pācittiya 104"
msgstr "pācittiya 104"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:358.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。不問比丘輒坐者。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc105" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:359.1"
msgid "pācittiya 105"
msgstr "pācittiya 105"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:360.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。不問主人便敷臥具。若使人敷。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc106" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:361.1"
msgid "pācittiya 106"
msgstr "pācittiya 106"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:362.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。不滿十二歲畜眾者。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc107" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:363.1"
msgid "pācittiya 107"
msgstr "pācittiya 107"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:364.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。滿十二歲。未作畜眾羯磨。畜眾者。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc108" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:365.1"
msgid "pācittiya 108"
msgstr "pācittiya 108"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:366.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。畜未滿十二歲已嫁女為眾。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc109" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:367.1"
msgid "pācittiya 109"
msgstr "pācittiya 109"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:368.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。滿十二歲已嫁女。不作屬和上尼羯磨。畜為眾。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc110" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:369.1"
msgid "pācittiya 110"
msgstr "pācittiya 110"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:370.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。僧與止羯磨復畜眾者。波夜提<span class=\"counter\">(一百一十)</span>。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h3>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:371.1"
msgid "<span class=\"add latin\">Chapter 11</span>"
msgstr ""

#. </h3><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc111" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:372.1"
msgid "pācittiya 111"
msgstr "pācittiya 111"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:373.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。弟子不二歲學六法。畜為眾者。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc112" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:374.1"
msgid "pācittiya 112"
msgstr "pācittiya 112"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:375.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。弟子二歲學六法。未作屬和上尼羯磨。畜為眾。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc113" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:376.1"
msgid "pācittiya 113"
msgstr "pācittiya 113"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:377.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。受大戒已不二歲隨和上尼。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc114" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:378.1"
msgid "pācittiya 114"
msgstr "pācittiya 114"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:379.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。畜弟子不與財法。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc115" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:380.1"
msgid "pācittiya 115"
msgstr "pācittiya 115"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:381.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。畜婬女為眾。不遠本處五六由旬。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc116" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:382.1"
msgid "pācittiya 116"
msgstr "pācittiya 116"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:383.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。畜未滿二十歲童女為眾。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc117" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:384.1"
msgid "pācittiya 117"
msgstr "pācittiya 117"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:385.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。滿二十歲童女。未作屬和上尼羯磨畜為眾。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc118" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:386.1"
msgid "pācittiya 118"
msgstr "pācittiya 118"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:387.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。畜孝女為眾。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc119" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:388.1"
msgid "pācittiya 119"
msgstr "pācittiya 119"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:389.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。畜將男女自隨女人為眾。波夜提<span class=\"counter\">(四十即不共中第四十)</span>。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc120" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:390.1"
msgid "pācittiya 120"
msgstr "pācittiya 120"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:391.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。畜惡性女人為眾。波夜提<span class=\"counter\">(一百二十)</span>。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h3>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:392.1"
msgid "<span class=\"add latin\">Chapter 12</span>"
msgstr ""

#. </h3><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc121" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:393.1"
msgid "pācittiya 121"
msgstr "pācittiya 121"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:394.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。滿二十歲童女。不二歲學六法。畜為眾。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc122" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:395.1"
msgid "pācittiya 122"
msgstr "pācittiya 122"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:396.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。滿二十歲童女。二歲學六法。不作屬和上尼羯磨。畜為眾。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc123" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:397.1"
msgid "pācittiya 123"
msgstr "pācittiya 123"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:398.1"
msgid "若比丘尼作是言。汝與我衣<span class=\"gaiji\">鉢<!--gaiji,缽,1[金*本],2&#x9262;,3--> </span>戶鉤。時藥時分藥七日藥盡形藥。我當度汝。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc124" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:399.1"
msgid "pācittiya 124"
msgstr "pācittiya 124"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:400.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。女人夫主不聽。畜為眾。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc125" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:401.1"
msgid "pācittiya 125"
msgstr "pācittiya 125"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:402.1"
msgid "若比丘尼語他言。汝二歲學六法。後當畜汝。若不畜者。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc126" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:403.1"
msgid "pācittiya 126"
msgstr "pācittiya 126"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:404.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。歲歲度弟子者。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc127" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:405.1"
msgid "pācittiya 127"
msgstr "pācittiya 127"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:406.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。宿作乞屬和上尼羯磨。畜為眾者。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc128" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:407.1"
msgid "pācittiya 128"
msgstr "pācittiya 128"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:408.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。作浴衣者當應量作。量者。長五修伽陀磔手。廣二磔手半。過是作者。波夜提<span class=\"counter\">(五十)</span>。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc129" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:409.1"
msgid "pācittiya 129"
msgstr "pācittiya 129"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:410.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。數數易衣服。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc130" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:411.1"
msgid "pācittiya 130"
msgstr "pācittiya 130"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:412.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。作衣極久乃至五夜。過是成者。波夜提<span class=\"counter\">(一百三十)</span>。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h3>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:413.1"
msgid "<span class=\"add latin\">Chapter 13</span>"
msgstr ""

#. </h3><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc131" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:414.1"
msgid "pācittiya 131"
msgstr "pācittiya 131"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:415.1"
msgid "若比丘尼。五夜不看五衣。波夜提。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="pc132" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:416.1"
msgid "pācittiya 132"
msgstr "pācittiya 132"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:417.1"
