#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:752.1"
msgid "應與不癡毘尼人。當與不癡毘尼。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="as4" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:753.1"
msgid "adhikaraṇasamatha 4"
msgstr "adhikaraṇasamatha 4"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:754.1"
msgid "應與自言治人。當與自言治。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="as5" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:755.1"
msgid "adhikaraṇasamatha 5"
msgstr "adhikaraṇasamatha 5"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:756.1"
msgid "應與覓罪相人。當與覓罪相。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="as6" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:757.1"
msgid "adhikaraṇasamatha 6"
msgstr "adhikaraṇasamatha 6"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:758.1"
msgid "應與多覓罪人。當與多覓罪。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h4>
#. <span class="add"><a id="as7" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:759.1"
msgid "adhikaraṇasamatha 7"
msgstr "adhikaraṇasamatha 7"

#. </a></span>
#. </h4><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:760.1"
msgid "種種僧中諍事生。如草布地除滅。應當學。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="51"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:761.1"
msgid "諸大德。已說七滅諍法。今問諸大德。是中清淨不。第二第三亦如是問。是中清淨不。諸大德。是中清淨。默然故。是事如是持。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h2>
#. <span class="add"><a id="conc" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:762.1"
msgid "Conclusion"
msgstr "Conclusion"

#. </a></span>
#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="52"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:763.1"
msgid "諸大德。已說戒序。已說八波羅夷法。已說十七僧伽婆尸沙法。已說三十尼薩耆波夜提法。已說百七十八波夜提法。已說八波羅提提舍尼法。已說眾學法。已說七滅諍法。是事入佛經中半月半月戒經中。說及餘隨道戒法是中諸大德。一心歡喜不諍。一學一道和合。如水乳合安樂行。如是應當學。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h2>
#. <span class="add"><a id="conc-verses" class="latin">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:764.1"
msgid "Concluding verses"
msgstr "Concluding verses"

#. </a></span>
#. </h2><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:765.1"
msgid "毘婆尸佛如來無所著等正覺。為六百二十萬比丘前後圍繞。說是戒經。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:766.1"
msgid "忍辱第一道　　涅槃佛稱最"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:766.2"
msgid "出家惱他人　　不名為沙門"
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:767.1"
msgid "式佛如來無所著等正覺。為八十萬比丘前後圍繞。說是戒經。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:768.1"
msgid "譬如明眼人　　能避嶮惡道"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:768.2"
msgid "世有聰明人　　能遠離諸惡"
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:769.1"
msgid "隨葉佛如來無所著等正覺。為十萬比丘前後圍繞。說是戒經。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:770.1"
msgid "不惱不說過　　如戒所說行"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:770.2"
msgid "飯食知節量　　常樂在閑處"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:770.3"
msgid "心淨樂精進　　是名諸佛教"
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:771.1"
msgid "拘樓孫佛如來無所著等正覺。為四萬比丘前後圍繞。說是戒經。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="53"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:772.1"
msgid "譬如蜂採花　　不壞色與香"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:772.2"
msgid "但取其味去　　比丘入聚然"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:772.3"
msgid "不破壞他事　　不觀作不作"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:772.4"
msgid "但自觀身行　　諦視善不善"
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:773.1"
msgid "拘那含佛如來無所著等正覺。為三萬比丘前後圍繞。說是戒經。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:774.1"
msgid "欲得好心莫放逸　　聖人善法當勤學"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:774.2"
msgid "若有知寂一心人　　乃能無復憂愁患"
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:775.1"
msgid "迦葉佛如來無所著等正覺。為二萬比丘前後圍繞。說是戒經。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:776.1"
msgid "一切惡莫作　　當具足善法"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:776.2"
msgid "自淨其志意　　是則諸佛教"
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:777.1"
msgid "釋迦牟尼佛如來無所著等正覺。為千二百五十未曾有僧前後圍繞。說是戒經。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="54"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:778.1"
msgid "護身為善哉　　能護口亦善"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:778.2"
msgid "護意為善哉　　護一切亦善"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:778.3"
msgid "比丘護一切　　便得離眾苦"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:778.4"
msgid "比丘守口意　　身不犯眾惡"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:778.5"
msgid "是三業道淨　　得聖所得道"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:779.1"
msgid "若人撾罵不還報　　於嫌恨人心不恨"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:779.2"
msgid "於瞋人中心常淨　　見人為惡自不作"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="55"></a>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:780.1"
msgid "七佛為世尊　　能救護世間"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:780.2"
msgid "所可說戒經　　我已廣說竟"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:780.3"
msgid "諸佛及弟子　　恭敬是戒經"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:780.4"
msgid "恭敬戒經已　　各各相恭敬"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:780.5"
msgid "慚愧得具足　　能得無為道"
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p>
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:781.1"
msgid "諸大德。已說波羅提木叉意。僧一心得布薩。"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "lzh-sarv-bi-pm:782.1"
msgid "十誦比丘尼波羅提木叉戒本一卷"
msgstr ""

